    <h2><xar:mlstring>ability - a simple style switcher</xar:mlstring></h2>

    <p>
        <xar:mlstring>Switch font sizes and stylesheets (for high contrast).
        Not too keen on the way this one works, as it disabled all other stylesheets to put the hight contract one in, which is a bit drastic.</xar:mlstring>
